verses.roman:
ei ta' kahiluṅ,-prabhu dekhi' vṛndāvana
punaḥ karilena yaiche nīlādri gamana

synonyms: ei ta' kahiluṅ—thus I have described; prabhu—Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; dekhi' vṛndāvana—after visiting Vṛndāvana; punaḥ—again; karilena—did; yaiche—as; nīlādri gamana—coming back to Jagannātha Purī.
translation: Thus I have described how Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu returned to Jagannātha Purī from Vṛndāvana.
